{"id":37487,"date":"2021-12-06T11:16:32","date_gmt":"2021-12-06T07:16:32","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=37487"},"modified":"2021-12-06T11:17:33","modified_gmt":"2021-12-06T07:17:33","slug":"prophet-given-kauthar","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/06\/prophet-given-kauthar\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Kawthar: The Prophet is given the Abundance in Paradise"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>A chapter was just revealed to me.<\/strong>\u201d The Prophet recited, \u201c<strong>In the name of Allah, the Gracious, the Merciful. Verily, We have given you the Abundance,<\/strong>\u201d (108:1) until he finished it. The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Do you know what is the Abundance?<\/strong>\u201d They said, \u201cAllah and His Messenger know best.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Verily, it is a river that my Lord Almighty has promised me in Paradise.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 784<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em>Hasan<\/em> (fair) according to Al-Albani<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650\u00a0 \u200c\u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633 \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0623<strong>\u064f\u0646\u0652\u0632\u0650\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0622\u0646\u0650\u0641\u064b\u0627 \u0633\u064f\u0648\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064c <\/strong>\u0641\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0623\u064e <strong>\u0628\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\